{"tid":252584,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"其實Band3都有band3既好","createTime":"2017-05-21T17:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T05:13:52.000Z","uid":43912,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfee483732e40a070620d896278cb97511bbb349","tid":252584,"uid":43912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T17:35:46.000Z","msg":"大部份band3都唔鍾意讀書同成績都唔好<br />\n係就係上堂果陣會搞下事 嘈d<br />\n但其實中學既生活係要瘋癲下<br />\n我覺得咁樣都係一種回憶<br />\n可能知道自己入唔到大學<br />\n所以將大學要玩既野提早係中學果陣玩<br />\n但係實有部份撚樣好自以為是<br />\n以為自己讀書好叻 不過叻極都只係band3<br />\n不過無論係band1定band3 始終都有好有壞<br />\n好似689同淋病咁 咪又係名校出身<br />\n亦都好多做地盤既 讀書係唔叻 粗口爛舌<br />\n但係佢地又何嘗唔係一個好錫屋企人既男子漢呢<br />\n所以 中學banding唔係最重要 <br />\n最重要係既係自己識唔識做人<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/E0fSCqeZ0PE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FE0fSCqeZ0PE&d=27wZqsYq1C8St8%2BHnNdl0whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b12b7052\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/E0fSCqeZ0PE</a>"},{"pid":"5aba4256226bdca0e7a6891f5305a27c6c4f408b","tid":252584,"uid":42764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:11:07.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書就早啲返工，唔好阻人讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有少部份想讀書既人就俾唔讀書既累死"},{"pid":"b5f82da9a81ef5e3e42054fb6c2baa8c65f4ceb8","tid":252584,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:25:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"458b786dfe8ed84a2da774d001169d8ff9f34de1","tid":252584,"uid":43912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係band3女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英雄莫問出處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33070479c9164d3e72cb71b620ba2c482ffb98f","tid":252584,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:16:30.000Z","msg":"Band3 但照玩照